humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The report indicates that out of 12 assessed lymph nodes, 1 was positive for metastasis (Axillary 1/12). This corresponds to N1 based on New Rule 12: N1 indicates metastases in 1 to 3 axillary lymph nodes (No/Total).

humanMachineDialogue.text: The report indicates that 1 out of 12 axillary lymph nodes were positive for metastasis (Axillary 1/12). This corresponds to a pathologic N1 stage.
